snippet.title: Falcon BMS 4.37 VR READY "and Beyond" Trailer 4K
snippet.description:
*Introduction / Credits*
Benchmark Sims is proud to present its latest production: Falcon BMS 4.37...

*New features*
The following features and improvements are presented in the video:

0:28 - VR Support
0:43 - New UI
0:46 - ECM Update
0:55 - CATM Simulation Fire
1:01 - MIRROR, F-15C WIP Systems, and Flight Model 
1:13 - And Beyond...

*Social links and websites*
DISCORD  - https://discord.gg/KQNHQBz
WEBSITE  - https://www.falcon-bms.com
REDDIT     - https://www.reddit.com/r/falconbms/

*Soundtrack Credits* 
La Corsa (2nd Version) - Luis Bacalov
